OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776946268
OL,3,CMurder investigation after 'amazing'
OL,4,Cveteran dies following assault
OL,6,FA 49-year-old woman who was previously
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of attempted
OL,8,Fmurder remains on bail.
OL,10,FDet Ch Insp Leanne Murphy said: "This
OL,11,Fis a tragic incident in which Martin
OL,12,Fhas lost his life, and our deepest
OL,13,Fcondolences are with his family, loved
OL,14,Fones and colleagues."
OL,16,FShe added: "We know the concern this
OL,17,Fwill cause across the community, I
OL,18,Fwould like to thank members of the
OL,19,Fpublic for their help, and those who
OL,20,Fhave come forward and assisted us with
OL,21,Four enquiries so far.
OL,26,@rD@aOUxD@LOU
