OL,3,CMurder investigation after 'amazing'
OL,4,Cveteran dies following assault
OL,6,F"An increased police presence can be
OL,7,Fexpected in the area, and I would
OL,8,Fencourage anyone with any concerns to
OL,9,Fcome and speak to them."
